  <main class='c8-center portfolio-page'>
    <h3>Overview</h3>
    <p>
      In my Programming for Web Applications class, I had to build a web
      application with a group that made use of an API. We ended up using the
      Spotify API for an application that creates recommended playlist for users
      based on their answers to a series of questions. It also allowed users to
      sign in with Spotify and save the playlist to their account.
    </p>

    <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
    <p>
      The application was built using Flask, the Spotipy Python package for the
      Spotify API, and Google Cloud Platform. It was deployed on GCP's App
      Engine and used Datastore as a database.
    </p>

    <h3>Timeline</h3>
    <p>Febuary to April 2021 (~3 months)</p>

